Initialize dc_num to 0
Display "Enter a binary number: "
Read input as bin_num
if bin_num is empty
    Display "Please enter a valid binary number."
else
    Iterate through the digits in the binary number form the right
        if the digit is not 0 and digit is not 1
            Display "Enter a valid binary number."
            exit()
        el the digit is 1
            Add 2 exponent digits position to dc_num
    Display "In decimal: dc_num"